{"tid":1599064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<<突發>>撕子狗扮學生畫花學校牆","createTime":"2019-09-27T18:31:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T19:28:23.000Z","uid":310434,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"928dd285ba967b3bf55eaa954bf23d74a48a4c85","tid":1599064,"uid":310434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T18:31:09.000Z","msg":"因為校內唔比整連儂牆，所以我哋學生就用校外嘅欄杆整咗個連儂牆，每整一次就搣爛一次，但我哋都貫徹撕一貼百嘅精神第二日再整過個連儂牆。<br />\n<br />\n去到今日（大約凌晨一點半發現)佢哋不單搣咗落嚟之外，仲用marker 畫花曬個校牆同將啲memo紙癡埋上去，仲想屈係我哋學生整到咁！但係可惜佢哋錯漏百出 寫字又寫錯仲要寫埋曬啲殘體字<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過都要讚一讚班藍絲嘅耐性<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋班學生都係學校附近留到12點幾先走，佢哋先走出嚟撕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eXxVdMw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeXxVdMw.jpg&h=ed40893e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QDmZFrw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQDmZFrw.jpg&h=55068975&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w398yMx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw398yMx.jpg&h=21b24a57&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DsoYbyd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDsoYbyd.jpg&h=8e13c322&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"758a6c5580b2d9e9aa21a54cbc367a449521d46c","tid":1599064,"uid":310434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T18:32:50.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"13ac3e357999e7b940420fb01e1b6c5db250e32b","tid":1599064,"uid":310434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T18:33:03.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"284d5596a8b50b2efa7a04801bc2d149c76ec31b","tid":1599064,"uid":310434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T18:33:16.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"59e4e53e25f294303335f406b1cdac5ff4b727c7","tid":1599064,"uid":310434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":